Description: This package implements the code and methods of the paper Elmasri, M., Farrell, M. J., Davies, T. J., & Stephens, D. A. (2020). A hierarchical Bayesian model for predicting ecological interactions using scaled evolutionary relationships. Annals of Applied Statistics, 14(1), 221-240.
